{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/travel/2020/08/21/暂住在蒙自.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"30f2ac43-2c54-5960-91f4-a9f610f85d01","excerpt":"暂住在蒙自 本来打算直接从建水出发前往景洪，无意间发现蒙自还有一个红河博物馆。本着好奇，反正建水去蒙自也就 15 块就启程了。 滇越驿站 在火车站乘坐 3…","html":"<h1>暂住在蒙自</h1>\n<p>本来打算直接从建水出发前往景洪，无意间发现蒙自还有一个红河博物馆。本着好奇，反正建水去蒙自也就 15 块就启程了。</p>\n<h2>滇越驿站</h2>\n<p>在火车站乘坐 31 路到州政府，就能找到驿站，客栈很有特色，房间都是设计成火车车厢，过道还展览着过去的车票和粮票，活脱脱一个小博物馆。</p>\n<p>驿站楼下是自己的食堂，点一份米线，汤肉和米线是分开打的，不得不说蒙自的米线更好吃一些。但我还是喜欢玉溪的凉米线。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/18504c6a523670741db0c473b6df7214/4b190/2020-08-21-1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/18504c6a523670741db0c473b6df7214/cbe2e/2020-08-21-1.webp 148w,\n/static/18504c6a523670741db0c473b6df7214/3084c/2020-08-21-1.webp 295w,\n/static/18504c6a523670741db0c473b6df7214/5ca24/2020-08-21-1.webp 590w,\n/static/18504c6a523670741db0c473b6df7214/d00b9/2020-08-21-1.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/18504c6a523670741db0c473b6df7214/a80bd/2020-08-21-1.jpg 148w,\n/static/18504c6a523670741db0c473b6df7214/1c91a/2020-08-21-1.jpg 295w,\n/static/18504c6a523670741db0c473b6df7214/1c72d/2020-08-21-1.jpg 590w,\n/static/18504c6a523670741db0c473b6df7214/4b190/2020-08-21-1.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/18504c6a523670741db0c473b6df7214/1c72d/2020-08-21-1.jpg\"\n          alt=\"旅店内部\"\n          title=\"旅店内部\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">旅店内部</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/c58a3/2020-08-21-4.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/cbe2e/2020-08-21-4.webp 148w,\n/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/3084c/2020-08-21-4.webp 295w,\n/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/5ca24/2020-08-21-4.webp 590w,\n/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/dad35/2020-08-21-4.webp 885w,\n/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/2baf0/2020-08-21-4.webp 1180w,\n/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/293e0/2020-08-21-4.webp 1500w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/a80bd/2020-08-21-4.jpg 148w,\n/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/1c91a/2020-08-21-4.jpg 295w,\n/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/1c72d/2020-08-21-4.jpg 590w,\n/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/a8a14/2020-08-21-4.jpg 885w,\n/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/fbd2c/2020-08-21-4.jpg 1180w,\n/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/c58a3/2020-08-21-4.jpg 1500w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/d78d654a4c929b712713a1ed62b986fd/1c72d/2020-08-21-4.jpg\"\n          alt=\"粮票\"\n          title=\"粮票\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">粮票</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/d2602/2020-08-21-5.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/cbe2e/2020-08-21-5.webp 148w,\n/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/3084c/2020-08-21-5.webp 295w,\n/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/5ca24/2020-08-21-5.webp 590w,\n/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/dad35/2020-08-21-5.webp 885w,\n/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/2baf0/2020-08-21-5.webp 1180w,\n/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/b33a3/2020-08-21-5.webp 4032w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/a80bd/2020-08-21-5.jpg 148w,\n/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/1c91a/2020-08-21-5.jpg 295w,\n/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/1c72d/2020-08-21-5.jpg 590w,\n/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/a8a14/2020-08-21-5.jpg 885w,\n/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/fbd2c/2020-08-21-5.jpg 1180w,\n/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/d2602/2020-08-21-5.jpg 4032w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/e2b49a3e0fa90e614872a062a80c9d4c/1c72d/2020-08-21-5.jpg\"\n          alt=\"车票\"\n          title=\"车票\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">车票</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>红河州博物馆</h2>\n<p>和云南的博物馆类似，先大讲特讲化石古生物，然后简单的几个青铜器，再就是法国的小火车，但是基本上只是简单的物品陈述。二楼是少数民族介绍，少数民族部分主要是一直沿用到 1950 年代的土司制度和少数民族服饰。其它的就比较少，比如各种少数民族的语言就没怎么提。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/7425ce9e645507e9e2c15b9f6e5f7cdb/4b190/2020-08-21-2.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7425ce9e645507e9e2c15b9f6e5f7cdb/cbe2e/2020-08-21-2.webp 148w,\n/static/7425ce9e645507e9e2c15b9f6e5f7cdb/3084c/2020-08-21-2.webp 295w,\n/static/7425ce9e645507e9e2c15b9f6e5f7cdb/5ca24/2020-08-21-2.webp 590w,\n/static/7425ce9e645507e9e2c15b9f6e5f7cdb/d00b9/2020-08-21-2.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/7425ce9e645507e9e2c15b9f6e5f7cdb/a80bd/2020-08-21-2.jpg 148w,\n/static/7425ce9e645507e9e2c15b9f6e5f7cdb/1c91a/2020-08-21-2.jpg 295w,\n/static/7425ce9e645507e9e2c15b9f6e5f7cdb/1c72d/2020-08-21-2.jpg 590w,\n/static/7425ce9e645507e9e2c15b9f6e5f7cdb/4b190/2020-08-21-2.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/7425ce9e645507e9e2c15b9f6e5f7cdb/1c72d/2020-08-21-2.jpg\"\n          alt=\"青铜器\"\n          title=\"青铜器\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">青铜器</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>蒙自海关档案馆</h2>\n<p>法国占有越南之后和清政府要到邮政权，在蒙自建立海关，蒙自曾经繁荣一时。在昆明铁路建成后，蒙自海关就名存实亡了。不过海关面向纳湖公园的部分还留了一部分楼可以开放查看文件。</p>\n<h2>康唯国际健身</h2>\n<p>喝了一杯「茶颜观色」就是茶颜的盗版，之后我买了 9.9 的健身体验，位置在中央大街附近，虽然没有玉溪的 1991 大，但是设备也很多，可以去练一下。</p>\n<p><figure class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figure\" style=\"\">\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 590px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/67ed8278fc386d1a29f9f58fbd4d7605/4b190/2020-08-21-3.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/67ed8278fc386d1a29f9f58fbd4d7605/cbe2e/2020-08-21-3.webp 148w,\n/static/67ed8278fc386d1a29f9f58fbd4d7605/3084c/2020-08-21-3.webp 295w,\n/static/67ed8278fc386d1a29f9f58fbd4d7605/5ca24/2020-08-21-3.webp 590w,\n/static/67ed8278fc386d1a29f9f58fbd4d7605/d00b9/2020-08-21-3.webp 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/67ed8278fc386d1a29f9f58fbd4d7605/a80bd/2020-08-21-3.jpg 148w,\n/static/67ed8278fc386d1a29f9f58fbd4d7605/1c91a/2020-08-21-3.jpg 295w,\n/static/67ed8278fc386d1a29f9f58fbd4d7605/1c72d/2020-08-21-3.jpg 590w,\n/static/67ed8278fc386d1a29f9f58fbd4d7605/4b190/2020-08-21-3.jpg 800w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n          type=\"image/jpeg\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/67ed8278fc386d1a29f9f58fbd4d7605/1c72d/2020-08-21-3.jpg\"\n          alt=\"健身房\"\n          title=\"健身房\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span>\n    <figcaption class=\"gatsby-resp-image-figcaption\">健身房</figcaption>\n  </figure></p>\n<h2>总结</h2>\n<p>蒙自的市区建设比较发达，随处可以见到直饮机。城市也很干净，物价也比较低。共享单车并不是大厂的牌子，自然不能免押金，而且有些需要预支付一定金额才能使用。从蒙自火车站出来可以乘坐公交前往市区，但是因为火车站的公交发车时间是按照火车行程安排的，所以一旦错过了一班公交就意味着这一班火车也错过了。</p>","frontmatter":{"category":"travel"},"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/08/21/暂住在蒙自.html","date":"August 21, 2020","title":"暂住在蒙自"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/travel/2020/08/21/暂住在蒙自.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/08/18/玉溪比昆明更加云南.html","title":"玉溪比昆明更加云南"},"frontmatter":{"category":"travel"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/travel/2020/08/23/滇南最后一个江南，建水.html","title":"滇南最后一个江南，建水"},"frontmatter":{"category":"travel"}}}}}